Software Version: 16.0.4312.1000
Official site: Microsoft
Language: English / Russian / Ukrainian

Treatment: not required

System requirements:

x86 or x64 processor with a clock speed of 1 GHz and supports SSE2 instruction set.

2 GB of RAM is recommended for graphics features, Outlook Instant Search feature, and certain advanced functionality.

3.0 GB of free hard disk space.

screen resolution 1280 x 800. To use graphics hardware acceleration, you need a graphics card with support for DirectX10.

Operating system: Windows 10, Windows 8.1, Windows 8, Windows 7 Service Pack 1, Windows 10 Server, Windows Server 2012 R2, Windows Server 2012 or Windows Server 2008 R2

Description: Microsoft Office 2016 well demonstrates how today has changed the approach to create documents and work with them. Many of us are beginning to work on the same computer, it continues on the other, as demonstrated in the third, simultaneously managing to make small changes for laptop, tablet or smartphone. Therefore, Office 2016 tried to make conceptually different. Almost all of the key elements in it have been developed from scratch, and applications oriented to a single style of work, regardless of the hardware platform. They are intended to provide the familiar functionality on any device, automatically adjusting its interface to the parameters of the current screen and the available system resources.

The composition of Microsoft Office Professional Plus 2016 package:

Microsoft Outlook 2016

Skype for business in 2016

Details of the assembly:
The assembly is a genuine Microsoft Office Installer with embedded updates and additional utilities that can both facilitate the installation and configure it to the last detail.
General information:
Languages: English, Russian, Ukrainian
Activation: KMSAuto Lite from Ratiborus
Extras: UBit Menu
Silent installation is carried out using the .msp files (MSP folder) and, if necessary, you can customize them to your taste by using the OCT. Details of the use of OCT can be found at the following link:

technet.microsoft.com/ru-ru/library/cc179097.aspx

During installation it is recommended to disable antivirus solutions - a process will take place much more quickly and the probability of successful activation is much increased.
Parameters silent install * (used AutorunHelper.exe):
/ O86U - silent installation of Office (x86) with updates
/ O64U - silent installation of Office (x64) with updates
/ O86N - silent installation of Office (x86) without updates
/ O64N - silent installation of Office (x64) without updates

/ V86U - silent installation of Visio (x86) with updates
/ V64U - silent installation of Visio (x64) with updates
/ V86N - silent installation of Visio (x86) without updates
/ V64N - silent installation of Visio (x64) without updates

/ P86U - silent installation Project (x86) with updates
/ P64U - silent installation Project (x64) with updates
/ P86N - silent installation Project (x86) without updates
/ P64N - silent installation Project (x64) without updates

/ UP2016 - install updates

/ KMS - activation
/ UBRU - installation UBit Menu ENG
/ UBEN - installation UBit Menu ENG
/ S - hide the progress window
For example, the team AutorunHelper.exe / O86U / V86N / KMS / UBRU
install Office with the x86 updates, UBit Menu ENG and activates all Office products.

For unpacked version (.exe) that is run as follows:
Install.exe -y -nr -gm2
"% WINDIR% TempOFFICE2016AutorunHelper.exe" / O86U / V86N / KMS / UBRU
Install.exe file name must be replaced with appropriate.
* Do not install the product at the same time a different bit (Office x64 and Visio x86).
